can be very\naccurately computed on all relevant scales up to the present time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2012 20:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Sep 2012 17:41:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2012 22:08:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-21"}
